### GET all trips
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trips

### GET one trip
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trips/GALE

### CREATE trip
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trips
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "TEST1",
  "name": "Test Trip",
  "length": "2 nights / 3 days",
  "start": "2026-08-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "resort": "Test Resort",
  "perPerson": "$499",
  "image": "test.jpg",
  "description": "Test trip"
}

### UPDATE trip
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/trips/TEST1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "TEST1",
  "name": "Updated Trip",
  "length": "3 nights / 4 days",
  "start": "2026-08-02T00:00:00.000Z",
  "resort": "Updated Resort",
  "perPerson": "$599",
  "image": "updated.jpg",
  "description": "Updated trip"
}

### DELETE trip
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/trips/TEST1